sourcesContent: import { useStyles } from "./styles"; import { Grid, Typography, Paper } from '@material-ui/core'; import { useState } from "react"; function Stats({ planet }) { const classes = useStyles(); const [name, setName] = useState('') console.log(planet); return ( <> rotation time {planet.rotation} revolution time {planet.revolution} radius {planet.radius} average temp {planet.temperature} ) } export default Stats
